### Request for Proposal for High-Temperature Industrial Printer
#### Solicitation Information
* **Solicitation Number**: WS3717573565
* **Tender Closing Date**: January 25, 2023 at 2:00 pm EST
* **Contracting Entity**: Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC)

#### Tender Details
* **Title**: High-Temperature Industrial Printer
* **End User**: Transport Canada (TC) – Aircraft Services Directorate
* **Location**: Ottawa, Ontario
* **Description**: Transport Canada (TC) requires the provision of a high-temperature 3D printer, including software, additional equipment, and associated training.

#### Procurement Information
* **Notice Type**: Request for Proposal
* **Procurement Method**: Competitive - Open Bidding
* **Selection Criteria**: Lowest Price
* **Trade Agreements**: Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement, Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA), Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA), Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement, Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement, and Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)

#### Contact Information
* **Procurement Authority**: Joanne M. Ladouceur (SPAC/PSPC)
* **Email Address**: joanne.m.ladouceur@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca
* **Phone**: None
* **Fax**: None
* **Postal Address**: None

#### Related Documents
* [View Solicitation on Ariba Discovery](http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/15092681?extsite=MTUwOTI2ODFfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==)

## Note:
All bids submitted after the tender closing date and time will be declared non-responsive. Please ensure to submit all required supporting documentation and bid submission by the deadline.
